files.description: EHI Export Data Dictionary — 8-page PDF listing 7 data tables (demographics, addresses, contacts, insurances, clinical/billing encounters, practice billing, practice clinical) with field names and SQL Server data types. Created 2023-11-28 by Michael Mai. This is the primary (and only) EHI export documentation for the product. Retrieved from Wayback Machine since the original URL returns 403.

Real World Testing Plan 2025 for b(10) Electronic Health Information Export — 5-page scanned PDF describing test methodology, care settings (ambulatory and post-acute), expected outcomes, and timeline (Jan–Dec 2025). Mentions export format as 'C-CDA files or FHIR APIs'. Signed by Michael Mai on 10/15/2024. Found on aarista.com/about/ mandatory disclosures page via Wayback Machine.
